Titolo: Britney's Dance Beat

Anno: 2002

Descrizione: Britney's Dance Beat is a rhythm game based around the music and videos of American singer Britney Spears. The game was developed by Metro Creative Graphics, Hyperspace Cowgirls, and Art Co., Ltdâ€“published by THQ. The game was released exclusively for PlayStation 2 on 8 May 2002 in North America and 14 June 2002 in Europe.
The game contains five songs: "...Baby One More Time", "Oops!... I Did It Again", "Stronger", "Overprotected", and "I'm a Slave 4 U". Successful play is rewarded with "backstage passes" which unlocks features such as backstage video footage of Spears. There's also a video vault. When players complete auditions they get backstage passes to unlock 360 immersive videos and behind the scenes footage. The game also includes various remixes during behind the scenes footage, menus, and credits. It also has photoshoots during credits. Versions of the game were released for Game Boy Advance on 25 March 2002, PlayStation 2 on 8 May 2002, and PC on 19 June 2002.



